
Scheduler Notification bot


What it can do ?
1. create scheduled messages
2. delete created scheduled messages
3. update scheduled messages
4. duplicate scheduled messages
5. deactivate, activate, scheduled messages

commands



SETUP:



DB setup:
alembic / sqlalchemy

1) Change db at alembic.ini

sqlalchemy.url = sqlite:///identifier.sqlite

2) database migration commands

1. Create migration file
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "your_migration_text"
2. Apply changes to db
alembic upgrade heads


